{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Wishlist The Game Today!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/Add_To_Wishlist_ENG.gif?t=1740175242\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/header3.png?t=1740175242\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every note you play adapts to your actions, creating a unique symphony each time. The game turns your gameplay into a spontaneous musical masterpiece.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Procedural musical puzzles that keep things fresh</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Harmonious compositions that sound great every time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> No combat, no timers, just pure chill</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/sort2.gif?t=1740175242\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">LightBreak is a unique musical journey that blends puzzle-solving with storytelling. As Ava, you'll use the mystical Saaz to create melodies that shape the world around you. From intricate 2D puzzles to immersive 3D environments, every aspect of the game pulses with music, creating a harmonious blend of gameplay and narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/tune1.gif?t=1740175242\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/header1.png?t=1740175242\" />Dive into Ava's silent world, where only music can tell Ava's story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Uncover a rich story about ancient artifacts, adventure, and family</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Enjoy a soundtrack that feels like a musical canvas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Solve musical puzzles to reveal hidden messages</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/cutscene1.gif?t=1740175242\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/header2.png?t=1740175242\" />The puzzles and hidden objects are more than just challenges; they\u2019re pieces of Ava\u2019s journey. The game\u2019s visuals, inspired by color theory and abstract art, react to the music, creating a beautiful, dynamic world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Find hidden areas and secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Piece together Ava's fragmented memories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Watch the environment change with the music</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/islands2.gif?t=1740175242\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1384970?t=1740175242","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1384970?t=1740175242","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/ef1887a3b7802cb34aa25019e7cf5c62444e9777/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740175242","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/ef1887a3b7802cb34aa2